actions.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Voice Vote.

official_title: A resolution designating room S-238 in the United States Capitol Building as the "Strom Thurmond Room".

summary.text: Designates room S-238 in the U.S. Capitol Building beginning December 5, 1991, as the Strom Thurmond Room, in recognition of the selfless and dedicated service provided by the Senator to our Nation and its people.

titles.title: A resolution designating room S-238 in the United States Capitol Building as the "Strom Thurmond Room".
